        </item>
        <item>
            <title>【教学】日元跌破新低旅游好时机，iPhone 锁定画面一键计算兑换率</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2025/01/08/travel-calculating-money-exchange-rate/life-tech/travel/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=travel-calculating-money-exchange-rate</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2025/01/08/travel-calculating-money-exchange-rate/life-tech/travel/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Oscar]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Wed, 08 Jan 2025 11:59:22 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[iOS App]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[实用技巧]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[旅游]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Apple]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[iOS 18.2]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[iPhone]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1284867</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>农历新年假期将至，大家有没有旅游的打算呢？最近日元又跌破新低，截稿前 100 日元约等于 4.92 港元，小编也「心郁郁」想去日本了。今日小编想和大家分享一个实用小技巧，能够在 iPhone 锁定画面一键计算兑换率，想在消费时快速换算港元价格就要看下去了。</p><div style="padding: 75% 0 0 0; position: relative;"><iframe style="position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; width: 100%; height: 100%;" title="0108 (2)(2)" src="https://player.vimeo.com/video/1044976294?badge=0&amp;autopause=0&amp;player_id=0&amp;app_id=58479" frameborder="0"></iframe></div><p><script src="https://player.vimeo.com/api/player.js"></script></p><div style="padding: 75% 0 0 0; position: relative;"><iframe style="position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; width: 100%; height: 100%;" title="0108 (2)" src="https://player.vimeo.com/video/1044971084?badge=0&amp;autopause=0&amp;player_id=0&amp;app_id=58479" frameborder="0" data-mce-fragment="1"></iframe></div><p><script src="https://player.vimeo.com/api/player.js"></script></p><p>iOS 18 前 iPhone 锁定画面下方预设为「电筒」和「相机」。更新至 iOS 18 后，用家可更改为各种自订功能。小编数学不太好，计算汇率时经常会「一头烟」。设定了这个功能之后，就不用再费神计算。启用「换算」功能后，无须解锁即可在锁定画面直接开启计算机，迅速进行汇率换算，省时又高效。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1285860" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/iphone_3-535x580.jpg" alt="" width="535" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/iphone_3-535x580.jpg 535w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/iphone_3.jpg 830w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 535px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲一键即可计算外币汇率</p><p style="text-align: center;"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1285861" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/img_1112-268x580.png" alt="" width="268" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/img_1112-268x580.png 268w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/img_1112.png 415w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 268px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲即时可以计算汇率</p><h2>Step 1 长按锁定画面开启设定</h2><p>如果你的 iPhone 有密码，你需要先解锁 iPhone，然后开启锁定页面，长按任意位置直至出现「Customize」选项后点击「Customize」。</p><p style="text-align: center;"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1285884" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/iphone_6-535x580.jpg" alt="" width="535" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/iphone_6-535x580.jpg 535w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/iphone_6.jpg 830w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 535px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲解锁后长按画面，点击「Customize」</p><h2>Step 2 更改工具为计算机</h2><p>现时你可以按照个人需求，选择移除电筒或相机快捷键，之后点击「+」，改为使用计算机。完成设定后点击右上角的「Done」。</p><p style="text-align: center;"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1285899" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/iphone_7-1-535x580.jpg" alt="" width="535" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/iphone_7-1-535x580.jpg 535w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/iphone_7-1.jpg 830w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 535px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲移除其中一个工具，之后点击「+」</p><p style="text-align: center;"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1285918" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/iphone_8-268x580.jpg" alt="" width="268" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/iphone_8-268x580.jpg 268w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/iphone_8.jpg 415w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 268px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲选择「计算机」</p><p style="text-align: center;"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1285920" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/iphone_9-268x580.jpg" alt="" width="268" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/iphone_9-268x580.jpg 268w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/iphone_9.jpg 415w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 268px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲看见 icon 变成计算机后，你就可以点击左上角的「Done」</p><br /><b>
]]>
            </description>
            <wfw:commentRss>https://unwire.hk/2025/01/08/travel-calculating-money-exchange-rate/life-tech/travel/feed/</wfw:commentRss>
