                <![CDATA[<p>在今年 CES 2025 消费科技展上，MSI 展出最新型号手提游戏电脑 MSI Claw 8 AI+ A2VM、Claw 7 AI+ A2VM，两部新机以升级处理器登场。两款新机均搭载 Intel Core Ultra 7 258V 处理器，结合全新 Cooler Boost HyperFlow 双风扇双热管散热系统，确保在高负荷运行下仍能稳定表现，为游戏玩家带来全新的使用体验。我们记者 Edward 就带大家到会场睇睇真机。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1285869" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/vlcsnap2025010818h11-2-694x528.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="528" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/vlcsnap2025010818h11-2-694x528.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/vlcsnap2025010818h11-2.jpg 1184w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1285863" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/vlcsnap2025010818h10-583x580.jpg" alt="" width="583" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/vlcsnap2025010818h10-583x580.jpg 583w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/vlcsnap2025010818h10.jpg 904w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/vlcsnap2025010818h10-144x144.jpg 144w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 583px" /></p><h2>Claw 8 AI+ A2VM：结合高阶性能与大萤幕</h2><p>Claw 8 AI+ A2VM 配备 8 吋 1920 x 1200 解像度触控萤幕，支援 120Hz 更新率，带来流畅视觉享受。机身搭载 32GB LPDDR5x 记忆体与 1TB NVMe M.2 SSD 储存装置，满足大型游戏运行需求。同时支援最新 Wi-Fi 7 和 Bluetooth 5.4 技术，提供高速稳定的网络连接。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1285864" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/vlcsnap2025010818h10-1-610x580.jpg" alt="" width="610" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/vlcsnap2025010818h10-1-610x580.jpg 610w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/vlcsnap2025010818h10-1.jpg 947w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 610px" /></p><p>该机重量仅 765g，电池容量达 80Wh，为玩家提供长时间的续航能力。介面包括 2 个 Thunderbolt 4 埠、microSD 卡插槽与音讯插孔。MSI 更内建 Windows 11 Home 作业系统及 App Player，支援运行 Android 游戏，进一步扩展游戏选择。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1285867" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/vlcsnap2025010818h10-3-458x580.jpg" alt="" width="458" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/vlcsnap2025010818h10-3-458x580.jpg 458w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/vlcsnap2025010818h10-3-scaled.jpg 710w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 458px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1285868" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/vlcsnap2025010818h11-1-472x580.jpg" alt="" width="472" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/vlcsnap2025010818h11-1-472x580.jpg 472w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/vlcsnap2025010818h11-1-scaled.jpg 733w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 472px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1285870" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/vlcsnap2025010818h11-3-520x580.jpg" alt="" width="520" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/vlcsnap2025010818h11-3-520x580.jpg 520w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/vlcsnap2025010818h11-3.jpg 807w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 520px" /></p><h2>Claw 7 AI+ A2VM：轻巧与性能的完美平衡</h2><p>Claw 7 AI+ A2VM 作为 Claw A1M 的后继机款，拥有 7 吋 1920 x 1080 解像度触控萤幕，亦支援 120Hz 更新率，适合注重便携性的用户。内建与 Claw 8 相同的 32GB LPDDR5x 记忆体与 1TB NVMe M.2 SSD，提供一致的高速性能表现。</p><p>这款型号重量更轻，仅 675g，搭载 54.5Wh 电池，支援 Wi-Fi 6E 和 Bluetooth 5.3，适合外出携带使用。介面同样包括 2 个 Thunderbolt 4 埠、microSD 卡插槽与音讯插孔，并预载 Windows 11 Home 系统及 App Player，让用户可灵活切换 Windows 和 Android 游戏环境。</p><p>资料来源：MSI, Unwire.hk<br /><b>
